text: Shkëlqim Troplini (1 October 1966 – 7 November 2020) was an Albanian wrestler. He competed in the 1996 Summer Olympics. On 7 November 2020, Troplini died of COVID-19 at the age of 54. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Albanian people Category:Olympians Category:Wrestlers Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Albania
